    <a href="https://confluence.cornell.edu/x/NZT9I" target="_blank">Linked Data for Libraries - Labs</a> and
    <a href="https://swap.stanford.edu/was/20250303124716/https://wiki.lyrasis.org/display/LD4P/"  target="_blank">Linked Data for Production</a>
